Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBAuditPermissions

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBAuditPermissions
public class JDBAuditPermissions extends Object
JDBAuditPermissions class is used to insert/update/delete the SYS_AUDIT_PERMISSIONS table. The SYS_AUDIT_PERMISSIONS table is used to record all changes to Users, Groups and Permissions.
